  <h2>
    <span class="">喜欢读&#34;疾驰的草原征服者&#34;的人也喜欢</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>


  <div class="content clearfix">
      
      <dl class="">
        <dt>
            <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/6755395/" onclick="moreurl(this, {'total': 10, 'clicked': '6755395', 'pos': 0, 'identifier': 'book-rec-books'})"><img class="m_sub_img" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/spic/s28344886.jpg"/></a>
